data.description: Great home in Hilldale School District! This nicely maintained 3 bedroom, 1 1/2 bath residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, privacy and convenience. With an additional shed 12x16 with electric. Along with an attached carport on driveway. All appliances stay in the home. With a large living room with fireplace and a spacious backyard. Call to schedule a viewing today and start making memories in your new home!
